cover comb
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a machine shearing comb that leaves a certain length of wool (cover) on the sheep in high country areas.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:winter comb
